{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"1":{"eng-name":"The Book of Purification and its Sunnah","ara-name":"كتاب الطهارة وسننها"}},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":267,"hadithnumber_last":666,"arabicnumber_first":267,"arabicnumber_last":666}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":658,"arabicnumber":658,"text":"حدثنا علي بن محمد، حدثنا وكيع، عن حماد بن سلمة، عن محمد بن زياد، عن ابي هريرة، قال رايت النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم حامل الحسين بن علي على عاتقه ولعابه يسيل عليه","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":392},"chapter":{"id":135,"ara-name":"باب اللُّعَابِ يُصِيبُ الثَّوْبَ","eng-name":"Saliva that gets on clothes","isFirstHadith":true}}]}